high_descs: Open right cabinet under sink, remove pot from cabinet, close cabinet.
Turn around, proceed to wall, turn left, proceed to fridge.
Open fridge, place pot on top shelf, close fridge.  Wait five seconds, open fridge, remove pot, close door.
Place pot on right side of table, to the right and above the bread, to the right of the white mug.
anns.task_desc: Chill pan in fridge, put on table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Open the cabinet underneath the sink and pick up a brown bowl from the cabinet.
Turn around, walk towards the door and then turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the bowl in, wait for a few seconds, pick it up again and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk straight to the wooden table with a loaf of bread on it.
Put the bowl near the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl near the bread on the table across the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around completely to face the gray marble sink.
Open the right-hand side cabinet under the sink and take out the pan that is in the cabinet.
Turn around, walk over to the door, and make a left to walk up to the fridge.
Cool the pan off in the fridge before taking it back out and closing the fridge door.
Turn around and walk up to the brown table.
Place the pan behind the bread that is sitting on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled pan to the kitchen table.
